BAT to Close Bremen Cigarillo Plant, Hamburger Abendblatt Says

-- B y   N i k l a s   M a g n u s s o n
-- 
2011-12-09T07:44:31Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-09/bat-to-close-bremen-cigarillo-plant-hamburger-abendblatt-says.html
British American Tobacco Plc (BATS)  plans to
close its filter cigarillo plant in Bremen, Germany, by the end
of 2014, which will affect 120 employees,  Hamburger Abendblatt 
reported today, citing British American Tobacco.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Niklas Magnusson in Hamburg at 
 nmagnusson1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Angela Cullen at 
 acullen8@bloomberg.net  